            "fields": {
                "heading": "What we supply",
                "body": "Vigil Care Staffing is a care-sector staffing agency that supplies vetted, directly employed workers to care providers across Greater London. We fill rota gaps reliably, whether you need a single shift covered or ongoing support. Every placement is matched to your setting and backed by a CQC-aligned recruitment and vetting process."
            },
            "provenance": "later_editorial"
        },
        {
